;             - http://msdn2.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms534885.aspx
; Note:       Requires Gdi32 and OleAut32 libraries.
;
;             Transparency rules:
;             A. The alfa value of the Foreground pixel is used to calculate the blending factors.
